    "HomeKit speaks HomeKit Accessory Protocol (HAP), which runs on top of a BLE/Bluetooth Smart or an HTTP/TCP/IP stack.  If an accessory does not support HAP directly a gateway is needed.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HomeKit speaks HomeKit Accessory Protocol (HAP), which runs on top of a BLE/Bluetooth Smart or an HTTP/TCP/IP stack.  If an accessory does not support HAP directly a gateway is needed."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HomeKit utiliza el protocolo HomeKit Accessory Protocol (HAP), que se ejecuta sobre una pila BLE/Bluetooth Smart o HTTP/TCP/IP. Si un accesorio no soporta HAP directamente, se necesita una pasarela."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HomeKit utilise le protocole HomeKit Accessory Protocol (HAP), qui fonctionne sur une pile BLE/Bluetooth Smart ou HTTP/TCP/IP. Si un accessoire ne prend pas en charge HAP directement, une passerelle est nécessaire."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HomeKit verwendet das HomeKit Accessory Protocol (HAP), das auf einem BLE/Bluetooth Smart- oder HTTP/TCP/IP-Stack läuft. Wenn ein Zubehör HAP nicht direkt unterstützt, wird ein Gateway benötigt."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HomeKitはHomeKit Accessory Protocol（HAP）を使用し、BLE/Bluetooth SmartまたはHTTP/TCP/IPスタック上で動作します。アクセサリがHAPを直接サポートしない場合、ゲートウェイが必要です。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HomeKit使用HomeKit Accessory Protocol（HAP），运行在BLE/Bluetooth Smart或HTTP/TCP/IP协议栈之上。如果配件不直接支持HAP，则需要网关。"
          }
        },
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "يتحدث HomeKit بروتوكول HomeKit Accessory Protocol (HAP) الذي يعمل فوق BLE/Bluetooth Smart أو مكدّس HTTP/TCP/IP. إذا لم يدعم الملحق HAP مباشرة، فستلزم بوابة وسيطة."
          }
        },
        "he": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HomeKit מדבר HomeKit Accessory Protocol (HAP), הפועל מעל BLE/Bluetooth Smart או מעל מחסנית HTTP/TCP/IP. אם אביזר אינו תומך ב-HAP ישירות, נדרש gateway."
          }
        }
      }
    },
